 * given a specific threshold. Uses 0-1 BFS.
 * 
 * @param n Number of nodes (as Int for indexing, safe since N <= 1000)
 * @param edges List of [u, v, w]
 * @param source Starting node
 * @param target Ending node
 * @param k Max allowed heavy edges
 * @param threshold The weight threshold
 * @returns True if an effective path exists, false otherwise.
